After the event, when you was informed that your call has happened, you have to go to the CRM to mark it “Happen”.  
Without this step, the call you created won’t be counted as your Bonus.

1.Find the Lead using Company Name or Lead Name and open it

![][image1]

2.On Company Card go to Communication page

![][image2]

3\.  Find Event type communication you created

![][image3]

4\. Edit communication you created   
![][image4]  
5.Make sure you check “Happen” box and save the communication  
![][image5]  
**\*if you don’t do it , your event won’t be credited.**
